claim.claim-text:
15. A method of constructing an item of furniture, comprising: 
providing a first structural component and a second structural component, said first structural component having a face, said second structural component having a face and an end; 
providing a bracket having a first leg and a second leg; 
securing said first leg to said face of said first structural component; 
forming a face bore in said face of said second structural component; and 
abutting said end of said second structural component with said face of said first structural component such that said first leg of said bracket is contained within said face bore and said second structural component rests atop said second leg of said bracket.
